==English==

===Etymology===
[[biology|bio(logical)]] + [[chemistry]]

===Noun===
'''biochemistry'''
# the [[chemistry]] of those [[compound]]s that [[occur]] in [[living]] [[organism]]s, and the [[process]]es that occur in their [[metabolism]] and [[catabolism]]
# the chemical [[characteristic]]s of a [[particular]] living organism

